<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الله عَنْهُمَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> <span class="c4">[مُحَدِّثٌ حَافِظٌ، اتَّهَمَهُ ابن الشَّرْقِي]</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">مَصَادِرُ تَرْجَمَتِهِ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c1">" الإِرْشَاد"</span>: <span class="c2">(٣/ ٨٢٦)</span>، <span class="c1">"طَبَقَات عُلَمَاء الحَدِيْث"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ٢٠٧)</span>، <span class="c1">"تَارِيْخ الإِسْلام"</span> <span class="c2">(٦/ ١٢٤)</span>، <span class="c1">"المُغْنِي"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ١٢)</span>، <span class="c1">"المِيْزَان"</span> <span class="c2">(٣/ ١٢١)</span>، تَذْكِرَة الحُفَّاظ<span class="c1">" <span class="c2">(٢/ ٥٢٩)</span>، "</span>بَدِيْعَة البَيَان<span class="c1">" <span class="c2">(ص: ٩٦)</span>، "</span>التِّبْيَان لِبَدِيْعَةِ البَيَان<span class="c1">" <span class="c2">(١/ ٣٩٧)</span>، "</span>اللِّسَان<span class="c1">" <span class="c2">(٥/ ٥٢٠)</span>، "</span>الثِّقَات<span class="c1">" لابن قُطْلُوْبُغَا <span class="c2">(٧/ ١٩٧)</span>، "</span>طَبَقَات الحُفَّاظ<span class="c1">" <span class="c2">(برقم: ٥٢٦)</span>، "</span>شَذَرَات الذَّهَب<span class="c1">" <span class="c2">(٣/ ٢٣٩)</span>، "</span>مُعْجَم المُؤَلِّفِيْن<span class="c1">" <span class="c2">(٧/ ٦٢)</span>، "</span>الرِّسَالَة المُسْتَطْرَفَة" <span class="c2">(ص: ٦٤)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>* * *<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">= أَبِي شَيْبَة فِي "المُصَنَّف" (برقم: ٩٥٦٠)، وَغَيْرُهُم.<br>(١) فَائِدَةٌ: ذَكَرَ لَهُ الدَّارَقُطْنِي فِي "العِلَل" (٦/ ٤٦١ - ٤٦٢/ ١٩٣٩) حَدِيْثًا، وَجَزَمَ بِأَنَّهُ وَهِمَ فِيْهِ.</p> </div>